query: SELECT DISTINCT fm.propertyId, p.addressLine1, p.city, dso.ds_probate as probate, COUNT(fm.id) as family_count FROM familyMembers fm LEFT JOIN properties p ON fm.propertyId = p.id LEFT JOIN deepSearchOverview dso ON fm.propertyId = dso.propertyId GROUP BY fm.propertyId, p.addressLine1, p.city, dso.ds_probate ORDER BY fm.propertyId;
